Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.79,0:02:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}史莱姆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.41,0:02:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}哎呀 难道奏会怕史莱姆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.71,0:02:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}才不是!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.13,0:02:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}只要我出手的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.25,0:02:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}史莱姆不过就是小菜一碟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.00,0:02:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.22,0:02:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}史莱姆软趴趴的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.55,0:02:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}和它们战斗的话就会变得粘答答的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.89,0:02:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}所以我才不喜欢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.60,0:02:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}用物理攻击的话的确会变那样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.93,0:02:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就用人家的火球和吐息
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.68,0:02:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}帮你把它们一网打尽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.48,0:02:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}安心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.98,0:02:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.19,0:02:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}塔妮雅真可靠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.48,0:02:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}再多夸奖一些也没关系哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.61,0:02:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}塔妮雅好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.65,0:02:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}塔妮雅最棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.24,0:02:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}一开始还想说这两个人到底会变什么样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.03,0:02:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但似乎处得很好的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.33,0:03:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}话说回来都没看到史莱姆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.96,0:03:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}如果是成群的话应该马上就能找到才对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.59,0:03:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}没办法了 从天空找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.30,0:03:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}天空?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.59,0:03:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}要请那只鸟去找吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.26,0:03:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不 还有奏和塔妮雅在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.64,0:03:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这次就同化之后由我去找
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.81,0:03:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}同化?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.08,0:03:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}等一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.79,0:03:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}雷因!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.58,0:03:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}雷因怎么突然像人偶一样断线了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.04,0:03:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}发 发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.88,0:03:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你们两个 我在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.96,0:03:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}雷因变成鸟了!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.21,0:03:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}虽然很类似 但不一样哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.51,0:03:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我将灵魂的一部分转移到了这只鸟上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.97,0:03:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}让意识固定在上面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.80,0:03:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这样的话就能自由地操纵鸟的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.27,0:04:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这就是驭兽使的技能之一「同化」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.77,0:04:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}顺道一提对话是使用魔力传递思念波
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.48,0:04:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}魔力…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.90,0:04:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}雷因居然那种事都能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.69,0:04:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真是难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.78,0:04:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是啊 这不是一般的技术呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.74,0:04:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.78,0:04:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}以驭兽使来说很普通…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.08,0:04:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}才不普通!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.25,0:04:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我 我去找史莱姆的群体
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.37,0:04:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在这段期间我的身体就拜托你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.88,0:04:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}雷因真是…相当的不得了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.63,0:04:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就是说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.85,0:04:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这也增加太多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.02,0:04:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我找到的时候也起了鸡皮疙瘩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.35,0:04:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}三两下就把它们收拾掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.90,0:04:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在那之前
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.40,0:04:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}雷因能用魔法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.28,0:04:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}如果是初级的治愈和火球的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.57,0:04:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}以前有试着练习过
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.20,0:04:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但能学会的只有这些
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.24,0:04:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.45,0:04:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.83,0:05:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你能用火球攻击那些史莱姆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.04,0:05:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}威力不怎么样哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.54,0:05:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}总之快点试看看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.50,0:05:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我知道了 别推我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.34,0:05:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}要跑到史莱姆群里了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.14,0:05:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我想想 将魔力集中在掌中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.93,0:05:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}构筑魔法的构造式
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.14,0:05:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.35,0:05:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}一口气释放!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.48,0:05:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}「火球」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.20,0:05:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这 这是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.99,0:05:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}一瞬间就结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.99,0:05:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}果然呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.74,0:05:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}雷因和奏订下契约
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.00,0:05:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}得到猫灵族的身体能力了对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.21,0:05:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}没错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.54,0:05:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}既然如此和人家签下契约得到的就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.05,0:05:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}龙族的魔力哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.97,0:05:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}人家的火球和吐息也用了魔力加强
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.39,0:06:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}龙族的魔力在最强种中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.01,0:06:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}据说也是第二高的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.31,0:06:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}而那个力量也现存于雷因的身上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.69,0:06:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}魔力…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.77,0:06:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}第二高?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.73,0:06:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不行了 思绪完全跟不上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.11,0:06:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}又来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.23,0:06:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}刚好呢 就拿它们练习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.45,0:06:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}魔法的使用比肉体更困难
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.70,0:06:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}还不能好好控制对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.16,0:06:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}话是这么说没错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.79,0:06:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}虽然可能很辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.46,0:06:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但请好好加油
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.08,0:06:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}毕竟你是我们的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.88,0:06:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}没错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.05,0:06:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我也要变得能堂堂正正地和最强种并肩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.88,0:06:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}想要更加地成长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.72,0:06:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}塔妮雅 请教我魔法的用法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.89,0:06:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}人家不会手下留情哦 做好觉悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.52,0:06:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}加油 雷因
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.85,0:06:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}加油
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.23,0:06:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}顺带一提 塔妮雅的教学方式…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.27,0:06:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}「火球」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.48,0:06:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}要让意识更加集中!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.74,0:06:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}姿势也要维持住!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.28,0:07:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}下一波要来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.49,0:07:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}快点 集中!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.74,0:07:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}「火球」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.04,0:07:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真的非常斯巴达
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.62,0:07:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}多亏了她 大致掌握了魔力的控制
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.34,0:07:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}猫咪大姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.59,0:07:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你在做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.30,0:07:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}因为完成工作所以来公会报告
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.51,0:07:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}龙族大姐姐 今天打倒了什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.97,0:07:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我们打倒史莱姆了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.14,0:07:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是妈妈说吃掉田里蔬菜的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.19,0:07:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}没事了 都已经不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.02,0:07:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}可以吃到很多蔬菜了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.99,0:07:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但我比较喜欢吃肉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.11,0:07:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}人家也是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.61,0:07:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.49,0:07:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}太好了!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.62,0:07:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我们都一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.83,0:07:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}让你们久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.62,0:07:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}报酬满多的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.67,0:08:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}大家都接受塔妮雅是装扮成龙族
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.09,0:08:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}有些奇怪的女孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.51,0:08:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}虽然有时候会差点泄漏自己的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.85,0:08:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但总之能安心了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.91,0:08:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}最强种连食量都是最强的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.58,0:08:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}吃饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.58,0:08:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}肚子好饱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.25,0:08:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这个镇上的料理也很好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.71,0:08:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你们两个今天都辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.01,0:08:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}虽然找到史莱姆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.97,0:08:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}还有把它们打倒的都是雷因就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.14,0:08:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}塔妮雅也教了我魔法的用法对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.85,0:08:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我才是受了很多帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.76,0:08:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那 那点事没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.02,0:08:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我们是同伴 这是当然的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.98,0:08:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}没错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.31,0:08:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}雷因是在哪里学会驯服的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.73,0:09:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我也非常在意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.49,0:09:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我觉得不是什么有趣的故事就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.20,0:09:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}有什么关系 人家想听啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.12,0:09:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我想听 我想听!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.91,0:09:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.12,0:09:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我是在故乡的村里学会驯服的力量的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.63,0:09:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那是个驭兽使们聚集的村庄
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.80,0:09:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我的父亲和母亲也都是驭兽使
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.97,0:09:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}所以我在懂事的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.59,0:09:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就自然地学会驯服了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.89,0:09:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}让奏看的御虫使的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.27,0:09:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}也是村里的人教我的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.19,0:09:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}虽然只是个无名的小村庄
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.69,0:09:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但曾是个好地方哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.57,0:09:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}曾?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.03,0:09:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我的故乡…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.32,0:09:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}已经不存在了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.87,0:09:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我 我不经意地就问了这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.79,0:09:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.25,0:09:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}没事的 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.88,0:10:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那个…虽然有点像是借口
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.71,0:10:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但我不是因为好奇心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.92,0:10:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}只是想了解关于雷因的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.89,0:10:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}人家也和奏一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.81,0:10:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}想要更了解雷因的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.68,0:10:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.10,0:10:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}如果觉得难受的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.19,0:10:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就不要勉强自己说了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.27,0:10:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我也觉得那样就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.02,0:10:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}因为是同伴所以想更加了解对方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.94,0:10:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我很了解这个心情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.90,0:10:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我也因为是同伴就想说出来…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.12,0:10:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我也想让你们两个知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.24,0:10:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你们愿意听吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.62,0:10:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我过去的经历
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.00,0:10:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那是我12岁时发生的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.30,0:10:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那天父亲和母亲都很忙碌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.38,0:10:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}没有办法看着我练习驯服
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.18,0:10:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}所以我在远离村庄的练习场一个人练习
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.65,0:11:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我练习到了天黑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.73,0:11:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}到周遭都暗了下来的时候才发现
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.86,0:11:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}明明是夜晚 但天空却被染红了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.45,0:11:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}感觉有些不对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.29,0:11:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这么想着的我急忙回到了村庄
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.37,0:11:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.34,0:11:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}当我赶到的时候已经太迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.47,0:11:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}村庄被魔物袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.51,0:11:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}幸存下来的只有我一个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.22,0:11:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在那之后注意到异变的冒险者赶到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.73,0:11:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}并且收留了我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.44,0:11:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在那之后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.69,0:11:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我就在帮助我的冒险者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.36,0:11:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}他们熟人的旅馆里工作
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.28,0:11:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}光是为了活下去就费尽心力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.53,0:11:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不断持续着那样的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.37,0:11:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在半年前的某一天
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.75,0:12:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我和亚利欧斯他们相遇了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.25,0:12:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}亚利欧斯?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.92,0:12:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就是勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.67,0:12:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}亚利欧斯他们刚好在寻找同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.47,0:12:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}便邀请我加入队伍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.22,0:12:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我马上便说了OK
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.68,0:12:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}想着只要和勇者们在一起的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.27,0:12:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我或许就能成就些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.35,0:12:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}或许就能阻止在故乡发生的那种惨剧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.15,0:12:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但实际上…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.62,0:12:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}亚利欧斯只是想要好用的棋子而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.00,0:12:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}抱歉 说了有些阴沉的话题
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.13,0:12:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}而且也很丢脸对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.01,0:12:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}奏?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.80,0:12:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我啊 一直都觉得很不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.89,0:12:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在你说要抓住盗贼团的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.64,0:13:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}还有和大王蜥蜴战斗的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.93,0:13:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}以及帮助我的时候也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.44,0:13:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}为什么雷因总是将自己置于险境
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.32,0:13:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}为什么要为了他人如此地努力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.41,0:13:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但我现在终于知道了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.45,0:13:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}雷因想要成为他人的助力对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.58,0:13:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}为了不让和自己同样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.87,0:13:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}有着悲惨经历的人再次出现
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.92,0:13:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}所以为了他人努力着对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.46,0:13:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}所以雷因一点也不丢脸哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.51,0:13:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}奏…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.72,0:13:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你就是人太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.68,0:13:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}该说是自我奉献过头
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.22,0:13:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}还是做得太过火了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.77,0:13:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}还是第一次看见做到这个地步的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.06,0:13:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但人家觉得也不坏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.52,0:13:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}也 也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.61,0:13:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}人家以你这样的主人为傲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.07,0:13:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}因为这就是雷因呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.16,0:14:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}自己的生存之道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.16,0:14:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就连那些日子…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.08,0:14:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好像都被肯定了一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.83,0:14:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你们两个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.34,0:14:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}话说回来…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.63,0:14:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}勇者他们是白痴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.97,0:14:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}雷因一个人努力地进行补给和支援
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.68,0:14:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}居然还说他没用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.35,0:14:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真是火大
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.47,0:14:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就是说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.64,0:14:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}雷因离开之后他们现在一定很困扰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.94,0:14:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}谢谢你们为我生气
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.65,0:14:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但我已经放下了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.15,0:14:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}才 才不是为了雷因呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.61,0:14:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}只是因为他们太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.53,0:14:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}塔妮雅其实很温柔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.69,0:14:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}快住嘴!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.61,0:14:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}脸红了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.86,0:14:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}才不是 这才不是因为那样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.24,0:14:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}现在只要能三个人像这样在一起就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.50,0:14:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我说 来比谁打倒的比较多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.63,0:14:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}哎呀 居然敢向人家挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.22,0:14:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真是愚蠢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.72,0:15:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.35,0:15:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}人家就接下这个挑战了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.64,0:15:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}怎么样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.56,0:15:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这次的委托是讨伐半兽人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.40,0:15:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}半兽人是等级E的魔物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.27,0:15:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}身体能力和哥布林没有很大的区别
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.57,0:15:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但半兽人的智能比较高
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.53,0:15:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}有会使用武器战斗的特征
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.04,0:15:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}照这样下去委托搞不好马上就结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.75,0:15:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你们两个可不能大意哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.25,0:15:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我们还只是菜鸟 没有什么经验
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.09,0:15:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就算对手只是半兽人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.09,0:15:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}如果有万一…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.09,0:15:38.55,Up,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.13,0:15:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我龙族的塔妮雅大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.18,0:15:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}怎么会输给区区的半兽人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.01,0:15:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}快点走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.31,0:15:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.60,0:15:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}要是不会节外生枝就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.03,0:15:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}塔妮雅 往你那边去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.61,0:15:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.95,0:16:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}轻轻松松
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.04,0:16:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}哎呀 是漏网之鱼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.55,0:16:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}等一下 这家伙是怎么回事!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.17,0:16:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}快放开!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.81,0:16:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}塔妮雅 后面!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.85,0:16:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}雷因!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.23,0:16:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你这家伙!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.36,0:16:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.23,0:16:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}流了这么多血
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.53,0:16:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.82,0:16:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我说过我能用治愈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.87,0:16:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}现在还有塔妮雅的魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.95,0:16:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}「治愈」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.00,0:16:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你看 完好如初
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.00,0:16:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.42,0:16:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}所以别摆出那种脸啊 塔妮雅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.96,0:16:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.88,0:16:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}因为人家…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.63,0:17:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真的已经没事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.26,0:17:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不会不舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.38,0:17:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.34,0:17:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}谢谢你们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.10,0:17:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}收集魔石回去公会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.22,0:17:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}收到!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.10,0:17:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}雷因就好好休息
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.47,0:17:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我来收集吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.18,0:17:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我就说我没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.07,0:17:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}久等了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.32,0:17:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}奇怪 塔妮雅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.32,0:17:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}刚刚还在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.62,0:17:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}总觉得她有些没精神
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.25,0:17:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好像…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.33,0:17:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}想要独处一下的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.30,0:17:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}人家在搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.88,0:17:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是龙族的大姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.55,0:17:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}今天打倒了什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.18,0:17:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}今天什么也没有打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.94,0:17:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.69,0:17:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.15,0:18:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}大姐姐有哪里痛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.32,0:18:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}如果觉得痛的话要好好说出来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.36,0:18:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}妈妈总是这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.87,0:18:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.12,0:18:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真是个好母亲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.33,0:18:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}虽然会一直叫我吃蔬菜就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.62,0:18:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}谢谢你为我担心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.04,0:18:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}人家没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.88,0:18:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}太好了 再见
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.84,0:18:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}她为我…担心了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.09,0:18:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但却什么都没有过问
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.06,0:18:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}因为自己是最强种族就自大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.77,0:18:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}然后粗心大意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.15,0:18:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}该以怎样的表情面对他才好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.81,0:18:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}雷因
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.27,0:18:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}塔妮雅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.40,0:18:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}雷 雷因?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.11,0:18:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.24,0:18:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.74,0:18:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那是…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.37,0:18:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}刚刚真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.83,0:18:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}人 人家…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.08,0:18:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}明明都这样提醒人家了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.79,0:18:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}却还是粗心大意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.21,0:19:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}还因为这样让你受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.67,0:19:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}虽然用治愈治好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.59,0:19:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但是只要有什么差错的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.88,0:19:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}所以!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.51,0:19:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真的很抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.89,0:19:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}什么啊 原来是因为那种事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.47,0:19:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}为什么你不生气呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.98,0:19:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}塔妮雅已经好好地反省了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.27,0:19:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}下次注意点就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.73,0:19:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}塔妮雅没事真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.36,0:19:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}奏也很担心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.40,0:19:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}塔妮雅 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.49,0:19:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}没 没事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.28,0:19:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是吗 真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.21,0:19:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那个 还是没有房间吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.96,0:19:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真是困扰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.00,0:19:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}想办法再一个房间就好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.97,0:19:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就算很小也没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.22,0:19:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不是责备我的失误
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.85,0:19:51.39,Up,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那就好好加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.39,0:19:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不 给我一间房间啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.05,0:19:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}也不是生气
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.60,0:19:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}居然是为人家没事而感到放心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.40,0:20:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真是不可思议的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.44,0:20:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}连床都让给了人家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.53,0:20:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}睡起来绝对很不舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.24,0:20:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}谁叫他是个滥好人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.66,0:20:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我只要塔妮雅没事就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.16,0:20:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这是怎么回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.46,0:20:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}雷因的脸一直在脑海里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.46,0:20:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}胸口暖乎乎的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.67,0:20:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}人家在想些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.84,0:20:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这简直就像…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.64,0:20:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}人家对雷因…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.27,0:20:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}鱼…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.73,0:20:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}才不是 才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.52,0:20:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那才不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.06,0:20:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}没 没错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.81,0:20:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}只是有点中意他而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.57,0:20:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}没有在那之上的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.40,0:20:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}人 人家才没有那么随便哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.16,0:20:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.16,0:20:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}要好好盖好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.37,0:20:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.29,0:21:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}晚安 雷因
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.71,0:21:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}有好多报酬 还有好多饭…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.09,0:21:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那是什么歌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.26,0:21:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}委托成功之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.81,0:21:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}最近达成了很多委托呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.93,0:21:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}差不多去买些装备怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.52,0:21:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}因为我们是最强种所以没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.40,0:21:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但雷因只是一般的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.73,0:21:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.32,0:21:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}回到镇上之后就去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.61,0:21:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这样就好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.37,0:21:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那晚餐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.62,0:21:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那就先吃晚餐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.49,0:21:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.58,0:21:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}快点走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.87,0:21:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好好好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.83,0:21:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}雷因?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.96,0:21:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.97,0:22:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好久不见了呢 雷因
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.44,0:23:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(100,100)}下集 驭兽使 VS 勇者
